flowchart TD
    Start([Client Request]) --> Method{Request<br/>Method?}

    Method -->|GET| CheckCache[Check Cache]
    Method -->|POST/PUT/DELETE| Master[Route to<br/>Master DB]

    CheckCache --> CacheHit{Cache<br/>Hit?}
    CacheHit -->|Yes| ReturnCached[Return Cached Data<br/>X-Cache: HIT]
    CacheHit -->|No| Replica[Query Replica DB<br/>X-Cache: MISS]

    Replica --> StoreCache[Store in Cache<br/>TTL: 300s]
    StoreCache --> ReturnData[Return Data]

    Master --> WriteDB[Execute Write<br/>on Master]
    WriteDB --> QueueReplication[Queue Replication<br/>2000ms delay]
    QueueReplication --> ClearCache[Clear Cache<br/>Pattern: /products]
    ClearCache --> ReturnSuccess[Return Success Response]

    QueueReplication -.->|After delay| ReplicateData[Write to<br/>Replica DB]

    ReturnCached --> End([Response])
    ReturnData --> End
    ReturnSuccess --> End

    style Master fill:#ff6b6b
    style Replica fill:#4ecdc4
    style CheckCache fill:#ffe66d
    style ClearCache fill:#ff9999
